        <title>About Me</title>
        <link>http://localhost:1313/about-me/</link>
        <pubDate>Sat, 23 Mar 2024 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
        
        <guid>http://localhost:1313/about-me/</guid>
        <description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;-hello&#34;&gt;👋 Hello!
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;I&amp;rsquo;m Ricardo, a Robotics student passionate about SLAM. This page contains more detailed information about my background and experience.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;-education&#34;&gt;🎓 Education
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Bachelor of Science in Robotics&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;
&lt;em&gt;Southern University of Science and Technology&lt;/em&gt; | Expected Graduation: 2027&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;GPA: 3.74/4.0&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Relevant Coursework: Robot drive system, mechatronics, control engineering fundamentals, Robot Modeling and Control&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;-technical-skills&#34;&gt;💻 Technical Skills
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;h3 id=&#34;programming-languages&#34;&gt;Programming Languages
&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;C++, Python&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;frameworks--libraries&#34;&gt;Frameworks &amp;amp; Libraries
&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;SLAM: ORB_SLAM3, OpenVins, 3D Reconstruction&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;C++:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Python:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deep Learning:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;tools--technologies&#34;&gt;Tools &amp;amp; Technologies
&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Git, Docker, Linux(Ubuntu)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;-honors--awards&#34;&gt;🏆 Honors &amp;amp; Awards
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;National Scholarship (2023) - &lt;em&gt;如果有的话&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;ACM Programming Contest - First Place (2022) - &lt;em&gt;如果有的话&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Dean&amp;rsquo;s List (2022, 2023) - &lt;em&gt;如果有的话&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;-resume&#34;&gt;📄 Resume
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;📥 &lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;path/to/your/resume.pdf&#34; &gt;Download Resume (PDF)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;-interests&#34;&gt;🌐 Interests
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;When I&amp;rsquo;m not coding, you can find me:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;📚 Reading about latest tech trends&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;🎮 Playing video games&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;🏀 Playing basketball&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;📷 Photography&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Feel free to reach out if you&amp;rsquo;d like to collaborate on a project or just chat about technology!&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
